
// --- Tags combined with embedded quotes ---

// Narrative: tag wrapping text with embedded quotes
<dramatic>"Madness!" she cried.</dramatic>

// Narrative: tag + quote in the middle
<whispering>She asked "why?" and ran.</whispering>

// Dialogue: tag + quoted portion at start
barista: <enthusiastic>"Try the latte!" she suggested.</enthusiastic>

// Dialogue: tag + multiline with quoted start
barista: <enthusiastic>"It's the best!" he exclaimed.
  I totally agree.</enthusiastic>

// Escaped opening quote with tag
<bold>\"This will be displayed with the double quotes included."</bold>

// --- Leading tag (space ignored) + embedded quotes ---

// Leading tag + narrative with quoted start
<dramatic> "Madness!" she cried.

// Leading tag + narrative with quote in the middle
<whispering> She asked "why?" and ran.

// Leading tag + dialogue with quoted start
barista: <enthusiastic> "Try the latte!" she suggested.

// Leading tag + dialogue multiline with quoted start
barista: <enthusiastic> "It's the best!" he exclaimed.
  I totally agree.

// Leading tag + escaped opening quote
<bold> \"This will be displayed with the double quotes included."

